reviews.text: This is a great place to have dimsum. Prices are reasonable. It can get pretty busy at times but this is to be expected.  The service provided was pretty fast and efficient.  They provide hot water and tea of course.  Apparently, the hot water is to wash your cutlery and bowl prior to utilizing it. The food was not too bad. We weren't too hungry so we ordered enough to fill us.

Quality food and tea with above average charge.  Visit here today as they are only opening dim sum at this mall around 0930. The only negative are the waitress service that ignore two empty tea pots and passing by several times and empty dishes kept on the table forever.  It keep me wondering my premium on dim sum could not exchange much better service than others local restaurant.
Excellent food and service
Delicious delicious
